Sensei, congratulations on all of your accomplishments. You are an exemplary role model that the children and the adults are lucky to have.

The book explains the 9 treasures very well and uses well chosen illustrations to compliment the text. The book covers everything from showing respect in the way you speak to being confident in and to recognize your "awesomeness". This is an excellent resource to help teach character to our students. Well done!
